==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Prettiness
<hw>Pret"ti*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or state of being
pretty; -- used sometimes in a disparaging sense.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A style . . . without sententious pretension or antithetical
<qex>prettiness</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Jeffrey.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pretty</ent>⟦br⟧
